title: Special Episode: My Interview with "That Viral Moment" - How I Gained 1M Subscribers In 1 Year
description:
I was interviewed by "That Viral Moment," a YouTube channel that interviews popular social media influencers to explore how they grew on their platform. In this interview, we take a look at the decisions and strategies I chose to start my YouTube channel rSlash, and how I grew it to 1.75m subscribers. 

Check out That Viral Moment: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XWCdoj7Vupw
